Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Health and safety
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407dtq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 May 1977
Growing number of health and safety warnings make everyday life a potential minefield. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less